---
title: Mumbai Beef & Spiced Chickpea Buddha Bowl with Roasted Veggies & Garlic Yoghurt
description: This bowl of nourishment will leave you feeling satisfied and energised in equal measure. Between crunchy cabbage,
roasted veggies and tasty Indian-spiced chickpeas, every bite is a delight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
